gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a42d6ed3136ad587e103e5f63f6949ef23717d3","tid":122153,"uid":714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"認真 成副身家買左阿仙奴反cup拎冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ba98004d0a371bcc2e498c241537bf046d107c","tid":122153,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真 成副身家買左阿仙奴反cup拎冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲爺爺要不敗 所以阿今年冇all in只係試水溫<br />\n等下年啦手足 38場不敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e08dabf0a43a06f5a83a0db9deb10a45533d4d8","tid":122153,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿狗無黑哨邊度入到一球丫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7624b7d75fde0207b300a6b7d98dfc3a4d4ea5f9","tid":122153,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf7e50e829926bcddbe68a71c79c4dc6977dcce1","tid":122153,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿狗無黑哨邊度入到一球丫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師兄你覺得個球唔係12碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外12碼冇判比拜仁係黑，但唔代表利雲踢高斯尼腳冇野牙</blockquote><br />\n扮公道扮足d<br />\n講埋個幾球手球先啦（係幾球）<img src=\"/asse